item.description:
Monday, February 25
5-9p
MetroHartford Alliance
31 Pratt St 5th Floor, Hartford

Free for members
$10 for non-members
Please register here: http://bit.ly/WfPtA4

Join us Monday night to work side-by-side with other Hartford area entrepreneurs! Working on a solo project? Our pool of regular attendees include successful entrepreneurs in software development, community leadership, marketing, and more that may be able to help you. Working with a team? Bring them along!

This will be a working session, please no solicitors or service pitches. Wi-fi, pizza, and beverages (including coffee!) will be provided.

Not sure where to park? Check out the Morgan Street Garage (just a few blocks away, $4 flat rate after 5pm) http://bit.ly/VLLkTi
item.name: HYPE Co-Working
